                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If you want to solo I usually would run by grab a razor and pull the two armors guy from in the building and kill them.  On a charm brk I would just get summon and then hit the zone out.
<br />

<br />
I would log on kill the 2 armor at the zone line and then go on my way.  I also kill the 4 armor guys on the bridge up top (2 at the lower castle and 2 at the upper castle).  I usually duo them as you dont have any easy way out on charm breaks.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
