                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If you want to solo,  I'd suggest the tents 
<br />

<br />
If you take a group or a few friends, I'd suggest the bridge between the two castle things on the way to the desert.  There are two sentries on either side of the bridge that seem to drop the water more frequently then down by the tents.  It's still rare, but they really do seem to drop more often there than down by the tents - at least that's been my experience for myself and helping others
<br />

<br />
The only downfall is the spawn times - we always ended up pulling mobs from the desert to exp on while waiting</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
        </tr>
