                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I soloed these waters from the 2 guards near the PoV zone out. If they are both yellow pull and root one then zone out and in, or pacify if white.  Charm and haste the nearby worm and set it on the guard. It will beat the slowed guard but you can always help with a nuke or two. Sometimes you will get the short unslowable guard pop. He is mean will beat the crap out of anything you can charm. I just kill him using the skellys. Charm a skelly, so you get lots of skellys chasing you and set your pet on the guard. Make sure the othe skellys see this. Now zone out. When you come back in you got a guard fighting a whole group of skellies he will lose. Wait for next pop. I dont recommend pulling the tents atm. The mobs warp on top of you before you can get them rooted. If charm breaks I get summoned then I zone out. If you cant handle 1 or 2 whacks then you probably wont be able to solo your saps in doomfire either.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
