                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have farmed 30+ sacred waters for myself (2 earrings) and friends.  
<br />

<br />
The drop rate averages about one an hour.  We pull the guys in the building by the zone out first, then named in plate from the camp, then named in chain.
<br />

<br />
When pulling a train from the camp,  we normally have one person hail a named near the zone out, and another person hail another named back by the rock on their walk back.  That way you have a second mob ready when the first is taken down.  You only need to hail them every 30 seconds or so to hold them, so you can hail, run back to the engaged mob and cast a few spells, then run back and hail the second mob to hold him, etc..</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 9px; line-height: normal">-----BEGIN ENCHANTER CODE BLOCK-----
<br />
<a href="http://www.therunes.net/forums/viewtopic.php?p=18979" target="_blank" class="postlink">Enchanter Code v0.2</a> 
<br />
E65.474/D h+ 4.2khp 5.8km ft15 G+++ e+++ o- T++++ L++ H++ f- g+ b c++ t+++ D- X- 
<br />
------END ENCHANTER CODE BLOCK------</span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
